97
00:05:10,367 --> 00:05:16,133
[SARI TERHIDU, MENGERUNG]

98
00:05:16,133 --> 00:05:21,033
Tuan Leon, awak perlukan apa-apa?

99
00:05:21,033 --> 00:05:22,867
[SARI TERHIDU]

100
00:05:22,867 --> 00:05:24,300
Jika anda akan menangis,
kemudian lepaskan semuanya...

101
00:05:24,300 --> 00:05:26,067
